{"serial": "62011", "department_serial": 56, "code": "GP3008", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Geographic Information System for Application", "ch": "地理資訊系統應用"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": [], "ch": ["廖啟雯"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["B", "C", "D"]}, "loc": {"building": "S", "room": "218"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 32, "department": {"ch": "地球科學學系", "en": "Department of Geophysics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 8, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "\"本課程希望透過手把手的上機實作，學習GIS軟體之操作與應用於資料蒐集與分析，學習成效之評估重點在於分組專題報告之討論與展演。\n\n1.藉由課堂講授及上機練習，熟悉地理資訊系統基本操作邏輯\n2.訓練資料蒐集能力，利用地理資訊系統將資料轉化為資訊並加以利用\n3.利用地理資訊系統進行資料分析並解決問題\n4.善用地理資訊系統圖形特性，成為Story Teller\n\"", "en": "\"The purpose of this course is to learn GIS operation and application for data collection and analysis by hands-on lab tutorial. The primary focus of course performance evaluation is discussions and presentations of a final group project.   \n\n1. Learning basic operational logics of Geographical Information System (GIS) by lectures and practices.\n2. Capacity building of collecting data and transform data into information using GIS.\n3. Data analysis and problem-solving by GIS.\n4. Become a store teller by utilizing data visualization capability of GIS.\""}, "outline": {"ch": "\"1.課程簡介及基本操作\n2.資料數化\n3.資料查詢\n4.主題圖\n5.空間分析\n6.期中報告\n7.影像分析\n8.網路GIS\n9.地球科學與GIS\n10.期末專題\n\"", "en": "\"1.Introduction and basic operation\n2.Digitizing\n3.Data Query\n4.Thematic Maps\n5.Spatial Analysis\n6.Interim Project Presentation\n7.Raster Image Analysis\n8.Web GIS\n9.GIS and Earth Science\n10.Final Project Presentation\n\""}, "textbook": {"ch": "1.地理資訊系統導論", "en": "1. Introduction to GIS"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradM